section.div: AI Agent that researches the lives of historical figures and extracts events into structured JSON timelines using LangGraph multi-agent orchestration.

KWeaver provides the tools to structure enterprise knowledge. Its open-source Ontology Engine builds, indexes, and queries a specialized knowledge network. You can embed this engine into any AI application to enable decision intelligence.
